'''丹尼爾·"丹尼"·霍斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Daniel "Danny" Fox'''}}，{{bd|1986年|5月29日|catIDx=Fox, Danny}}）是一名在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生的[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[後衛_(足球)|左閘]]或[[中場#翼鋒|左翼]]，目前為自由身。

霍斯曾代表[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]參加國際賽，其後轉籍代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭成年隊]]，於2009年11月負於[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]首次上陣。

==生平==
===球會===
;愛華頓
霍斯在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[柴郡|柴郡]]的[[民政教區|民政教區]][[Winsford|温斯福德]]（Winsford）出生，出身於[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]的青訓系統，2004年5月簽署[[職業|職業]]合約，僅曾於10月主場對[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]獲選為一隊沒有上陣的後補球員，時年18歲。

;外借斯特蘭拉爾
他於2005年獲外借到[[蘇乙|蘇乙]]球會[[斯特蘭拉爾足球會|斯特蘭拉爾]]，期間上陣11場，在對[[伯立克流浪者足球俱乐部|伯威克]]（Berwick Rangers）射入1球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_div_1/4306171.stm |title=Berwick Rangers 1–2 Stranraer 
|publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=1 March 2005 |accessdate=29 December 2009}}</ref>，並協助球隊獲得聯賽亞軍及取得升班[[蘇甲|蘇甲]]的資格。2005年夏季他遭愛華頓棄用。

;華素爾
[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|華素爾]]隨即羅致霍斯，簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11671_2337965,00.html |title=Fox to join Saddlers |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-06-02 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308023451/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11671_2337965,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。效力期間在各項賽事上陣超過100場。2006/07年球季華素爾獲得[[英格蘭足球聯賽|乙組〈第四級〉聯賽]]冠軍及升班甲組〈第三級〉。他與[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]在2008年1月[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]期間扯上關係，據報列斯聯提出連同附加條款的30萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]出價被華素爾一口回絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/United-move-for-transfer-targets.3629991.jp |title=United move for transfer targets |publisher=''yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk'' |date=2007-12-31 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2009-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727132912/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/United-move-for-transfer-targets.3629991.jp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但合約將於球季結束後屆滿的霍斯拒絕簽署球會提供的新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/7170331.stm |title=Fox stalls on new Saddlers deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-01-03 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2019-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910232629/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/7170331.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。霍斯雖然在季後約滿，由於未滿24歲，華素爾仍然可以向其加盟的球會收取補償金。

;高雲地利
華素爾一度接納[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]沒有透露金額的出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/7186978.stm |title=Walsall accept U's offer for Fox |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-01-14 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914125005/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/7186978.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]後發先至<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_3071404,00.html |title=Coventry in talks with Fox |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2008-01-22 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2008-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080406012416/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_3071404,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成功與華素爾達成交易金額，在2008年1月28日將霍斯收歸旗下<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/7213596.stm |title=Fox completes move to Coventry |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-01-28 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2008-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080131151318/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/7213596.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，簽約三年半，72小時後，霍斯的隊友[[史葛·丹恩|史葛·丹恩]]（Scott Dann）亦追隨其後轉投[[理光運動場|理光運動場]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/7221411.stm |title=Coventry sign Dann from Walsall |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-02-01 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124070340/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/7221411.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，兩人身價合計約110萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/7416703.stm |title=New Walsall boss gets cash boost |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-05-23 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913050023/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/7416703.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年4月26日霍斯入選「[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英冠|英冠]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8019726.stm |title=Giggs earns prestigious PFA award |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-04-26 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2019-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323131353/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8019726.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;些路迪
2009年7月16日[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]出價約200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]希望將霍斯帶到[[城市足球場|城市足球場]]，但被高雲地利拒絕。7月23日高雲地利接納[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]的出價，霍斯前赴[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]][[凯尔特人公园球场|凯尔特人公园球场]]接受體測<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12874_5450381,00.html |title=Celtic look to catch Fox |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310093948/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12874_5450381,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他於翌日簽署合約，為期四年半，轉會費沒有透露，但據報為150萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref name="Celtic sign Coventry defender Fox">{{cite news |language=en |title=Celtic sign Coventry defender Fox |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/celtic/8166242.stm |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=24 July 2009 |accessdate=14 January 2010}}</ref><ref name="Celtic snare Fox">{{cite news |language=en |title=Celtic snare Fox |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11787_5451775,00.html |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=24 July 2009 |accessdate=14 January 2010 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070718/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11787_5451775,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隨即安排在[[溫布萊盃|溫布萊盃]]（Wembley Cup）上陣出戰[[阿赫利体育俱乐部|艾哈利]]。

霍斯為些路迪上陣首場競爭性賽事是2009年7月29日在[[2009/10赛季欧洲冠军联赛#外圍賽第三圈|歐聯外圍賽]]主場0-1負於[[莫斯科迪纳摩足球俱乐部|莫斯科戴拿模]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/8173689.stm |title=Celtic 0-1 Dinamo Moscow |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-07-29 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121134318/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/8173689.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他更負責主踢[[自由球|自由球]]的任務，但沒有直接取得入球，只曾在對[[圣庄士东足球俱乐部|聖莊士東]]及[[邓迪联足球俱乐部|登地聯]]交出數次助攻<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/8210620.stm |title=Celtic 5 – 2 St. Johnstone |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=22 August 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/8249319.stm |title=Celtic 1–1 Dundee United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=12 September 2009}}</ref>。

;般尼
在[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]僅逗留了6個月，2010年1月29日霍斯返回[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]加盟新升[[英超|英超]]的[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]，簽約三年半，轉會費沒有透露，相信金額為180萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8485230.stm |title=Celtic defender Danny Fox agrees Burnley deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=29 January 2010|accessdate=29 January 2010}}</ref>。2月6日首次上陣主場對[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，霍斯交出1次助攻外，更射入奠勝球以2-1取勝，並壓過對手脫離降班區域<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8497953.stm |title=Burnley 2–1 West Ham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=6 February 2010 |accessdate=6 February 2010}}</ref>。但最終般尼由於整體實力不足，僅在英超一季便降班返回[[英冠|英冠]]。霍斯隨隊降班在[[英冠|英冠]]角逐一個球季，但未能取得升班資格。

;修咸頓
2011年8月11日於英冠球季剛展開一輪賽事後，霍斯轉投新升班[[英冠|英冠]]的[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]，轉會費沒有透露，簽約四年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14494862.stm |title=Southampton sign Danny Fox from Burnley for undisclosed fee |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-11 |accessdate=2011-08-12 |archive-date=2011-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901185937/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14494862.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;外借諾定咸森林
2014年1月30日，[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]將霍斯外借到[[英冠|英冠]]的[[諾定咸森林|諾定咸森林]]，借用期至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/25963384 |title=Transfer window: Southampton's Danny Fox joins Forest on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-01-30 |accessdate=2015-04-07 |archive-date=2014-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312201505/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/25963384 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;諾定咸森林
2014年5月9日，[[諾定咸森林|諾定咸森林]]免轉會費從[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]正式簽入霍斯，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/27351374 |title=Nottingham Forest: Danny Fox joins on three-year deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-05-09 |accessdate=2015-04-07 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924204209/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/27351374 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
霍斯與[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]隊友一史葛·丹恩同獲[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]徵召備戰於2008年3月25日對[[波蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|波蘭]]的賽事，霍斯正選上陣並踢足全場90分鐘<ref name="Fox and Dann make Under-21 debut">{{cite news |language=en |title=Fox and Dann make Under-21 debut |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/7314234.stm |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=26 March 2008 |accessdate=26 August 2009}}</ref>。

同年年尾霍斯宣佈以其[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[祖父|祖父]]的血緣可以代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭國家隊]]參賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/football/world-football/2008/12/28/coventry-ace-danny-fox-admits-he-d-love-to-play-in-dark-blue-of-scotland-86908-21000351/ |title=Coventry ace Danny Fox admits he'd love to play in dark blue of Scotland |publisher=''dailyrecord.co.uk'' |date=2008-12-28 |accessdate=2011-}}</ref>，他入選2009年10月對[[日本國家足球隊|日本]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/8284355.stm |title=Fox earns first Scotland call-up |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=2009-10-01 |accessdate=2011-01-27}}</ref>，但在為[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]上陣時受傷而退隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/football/scotland/2009/10/06/delight-for-lee-wallace-after-finally-getting-cap-call-86908-21726631/ |title=Delight for Lee Wallace after finally getting cap call |publisher=''dailyrecord.co.uk'' |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2012-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218021618/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/football/scotland/2009/10/06/delight-for-lee-wallace-after-finally-getting-cap-call-86908-21726631/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。霍斯最終在11月14日首次代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]上陣，作客[[卡迪夫城運動場|卡迪夫城運動場]]以0-3敗於[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]腳下<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8344879.stm |title=Wales 3-0 Scotland |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-11-14 |accessdate=2011-01-27 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109005334/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8344879.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

